---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="SMS Account Notifications Opt-In | RevAgentic" description="Consent to receive account update notifications from RevAgentic (Agentic Revenue Lab LLC).">
<nav class="border-b border-brand-border bg-white px-6 py-4">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <span class="font-display font-bold text-brand-navy">revagentic<span class="text-brand-purple">.ai</span></span>
  </div>
</nav>
<main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">

  <div class="bg-brand-bg border border-brand-border rounded-2xl p-8 mb-10">
    <p class="text-xs font-mono text-brand-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Message Sender</p>
    <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl text-brand-navy mb-1">RevAgentic</h1>
    <p class="text-brand-muted font-body text-sm">Agentic Revenue Lab LLC &nbsp;·&nbsp; hello@revagentic.ai &nbsp;·&nbsp; Chicago, IL</p>
  </div>

  <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-4">Account Notifications Opt-In</h2>
  <p class="text-brand-muted font-body leading-relaxed mb-8">
    RevAgentic (Agentic Revenue Lab LLC) sends account update notifications to gym and fitness business operators who submit a Revenue Systems Diagnostic request on revagentic.ai. Before any message is sent, the operator is shown the following opt-in at the point of form submission:
  </p>

  <div class="border-2 border-brand-purple rounded-2xl p-8 mb-10">
    <p class="font-display font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-4 text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">Opt-In — As Shown to Users at Point of Submission</p>
    <div class="bg-white border border-brand-border rounded-xl p-6 mb-4">
      <label class="flex items-start gap-3">
        bg-white\">
        <span class="text-brand-muted font-body text-sm leading-relaxed">
          I agree to receive account update notifications from <strong>RevAgentic (Agentic Revenue Lab LLC)</strong> at the phone number provided. Msg &amp; data rates may apply. Reply <strong>STOP</strong> to opt out at any time. Reply <strong>HELP</strong> for help. See <a href="/privacy" class="text-brand-purple underline">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="/terms" class="text-brand-purple underline">Terms</a>.
        </span>
      </label>
    </div>
    <p class="text-xs text-brand-muted font-body">Users must actively check this box before submitting. Consent is never a condition of purchase.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-xl text-brand-navy mb-4">Account Notifications You Will Receive</h3>
    <ul class="space-y-3">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-muted font-body text-sm leading-relaxed">
        <span class="text-brand-purple font-bold mt-0.5">→</span>
        A notification that your Revenue Systems Diagnostic report is ready for review
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-brand-muted font-body text-sm leading-relaxed">
        <span class="text-brand-purple font-bold mt-0.5">→</span>
        Account status updates related to your submitted diagnostic request
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-xl text-brand-navy mb-4">How to Opt Out</h3>
    <p class="text-brand-muted font-body leading-relaxed">Reply <strong>STOP</strong> to any message to unsubscribe immediately. Reply <strong>START</strong> to resubscribe. Reply <strong>HELP</strong> or email <a href="mailto:hello@revagentic.ai" class="text-brand-purple hover:underline">hello@revagentic.ai</a> for assistance.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-xl text-brand-navy mb-4">SMS Number</h3>
    <p class="text-brand-muted font-body leading-relaxed">Account notifications are sent from <strong>+1 (855) 905-5409</strong>, operated by Agentic Revenue Lab LLC. Standard message and data rates may apply.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-xl text-brand-navy mb-4">Privacy</h3>
    <p class="text-brand-muted font-body leading-relaxed">Your phone number will never be sold or shared with third parties. See our <a href="/privacy" class="text-brand-purple hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="/terms" class="text-brand-purple hover:underline">Terms of Service</a>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-brand-border pt-8">
    <p class="text-brand-muted font-body text-sm"><strong>Agentic Revenue Lab LLC</strong> d/b/a RevAgentic &nbsp;·&nbsp; hello@revagentic.ai &nbsp;·&nbsp; Chicago, IL</p>
  </div>
</main>
<footer class="border-t border-brand-border px-6 py-8 bg-white mt-16">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-brand-muted text-sm">
    <p>© 2026 RevAgentic. All rights reserved. RevAgentic is a service of Agentic Revenue Lab LLC.</p>
  </div>
</footer>
</Layout>